---
import Shell from "../layouts/Shell.astro";
---

<Shell
  title="VADIM KUZNETSOV"
  description="Вадим Кузнецов — full-stack разработчик. Проекты, эксперименты, утилиты."
>
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[var(--color-ink-dim)]">
    <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-base normal-case tracking-normal text-[var(--color-neon-cyan)]">
      &gt;_ vvadimkuznetsovv
    </span>
    <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-base normal-case tracking-normal">
      online · v0.1
    </span>
  </header>

  <section class="mt-20 sm:mt-28">
    <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-lg text-[var(--color-neon-magenta)] sm:text-xl">
      // identity
    </p>

    <h1
      class="mt-3 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-[clamp(2.4rem,9vw,6.5rem)] leading-[0.95] text-[var(--color-ink-bone)] [text-shadow:0_0_30px_rgba(0,240,255,0.25)]"
    >
      vadim<br />kuznetsov
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-[family-name:var(--font-ui)] text-base text-[var(--color-ink-haze)] sm:text-lg"
    >
      full-stack разработчик. строю веб, мобильное, игры. ниже&nbsp;— живые проекты.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-16 sm:mt-24">
    <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-lg text-[var(--color-neon-cyan)]">
      // запуски
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <a
        href="/traffic-laws/"
        class="group relative block overflow-hidden border border-[var(--color-neon-cyan)] bg-[var(--color-bg-deck)] p-5 transition-[transform,box-shadow] duration-200 hover:-translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-[0_0_0_1px_var(--color-neon-cyan),0_0_30px_rgba(0,240,255,0.35)] sm:p-7"
        style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, calc(100% - 18px) 0, 100% 18px, 100% 100%, 18px 100%, 0 calc(100% - 18px));"
      >
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-ui)] text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-ink-bone)] sm:text-2xl">
            traffic-laws
          </h2>
          <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-base text-[var(--color-neon-amber)]">
            WIP
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-haze)] sm:text-base">
          Уникальный сайт изучения ПДД категории B: подробные объяснения каждого ответа,
          разбор картинок, киберпанк‑роман с вшитыми правилами.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-base text-[var(--color-neon-cyan)] transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">
          → open /traffic-laws/
        </p>
      </a>

      <div class="border border-dashed border-[var(--color-ink-dim)] bg-[var(--color-bg-deck)]/40 p-5 text-sm text-[var(--color-ink-dim)] sm:p-6">
        <span class="font-[family-name:var(--font-hud)] text-base text-[var(--color-neon-magenta)]">
          // soon
        </span>
        <p class="mt-2">
          полное портфолио: <span class="text-[var(--color-ink-haze)]">кондиционеркин23.рф</span>,
          <span class="text-[var(--color-ink-haze)]">print.kubstu.ru</span>,
          <span class="text-[var(--color-ink-haze)]">proverka-cheka.online</span>,
          <span class="text-[var(--color-ink-haze)]">Fearful Obscured Grounds</span>
          — наполню после релиза traffic-laws.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="mt-24 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-[var(--color-bg-rack)] pt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--color-ink-dim)]">
    <span>// {new Date().getFullYear()}</span>
    <a
      class="text-[var(--color-neon-cyan)] hover:text-[var(--color-ink-bone)]"
      href="https://github.com/vvadimkuznetsovv"
      rel="noreferrer noopener"
      target="_blank">github</a
    >
  </footer>
</Shell>
